**ttak_tam_tam**
- [ narukkāṇi ]
s. the state of being small and stunted as a child
கரளை
நருவாணி
[ nrukkāṇi ]
s. the state of being small and stunted
as a boy or girl
காளை. பார். நசுக்கான். (c.)
பெ. நருங்கு. being small and stunted
as a child; கறளை. (w.)

**சென்னைப் பல்கலைக்கழகத் தமிழ்ப் பேரகராதி**
- - narukkāṇi;
- n. <</>நருங்கு-.
- Being small and stunted;  as a child;
- கறளை. (W.)

